														</div>
			</div>
			<div class="content" id="post-content-4045537">
									

<p>While I appreciate the attempts to gross me out, they do not work as expected. This also doesn't help the mediocre story being told here which I feel is nothing new. Seen so many &quot;fellas we gotta kill 096/other unkillable lad&quot; stories that nothing feels original anymore. Maybe if this was more revolting I'd like it, but as it stands, I can't bring myself to like this.</p>

