<p>So yeah, it's the weirdest damn thing. I made this three and a half years ago when I was a relative newbie, before I had successfully posted anything yet alone was a regular contributor. I can't say it's not a knockoff of 682's log, and I can't say it's good either, which is why I abandoned it shortly after making it.</p>
